 culty members of UT Health Austin Pediatric Neurosciences at Dell Children
 ’s. Each presentation provides specific techniques and evidence-based reco
 mmendations for diagnosis and management of neurological conditions common
 ly encountered by the general pediatrician. Registration for both in-perso
 n and virtual attendance is free. Register and learn more » For questions\
 , email pediatricneurosciences@ascension.org .\\n\\nRegister »: https://as
 cension-ce-cme.cloud-cme.com/course/courseoverview?P=0&EID=34791\\nRegiste
 r and learn more »: http://ascension-ce-cme.cloud-cme.com/course/courseove
 rview?P=0&EID=34791\\n\\nEvent page: https://dellmed.utexas.edu/events/7th
